data.description: MOVE IN READY! Assumable VA loan.Nestled in the heart of Crestview, this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and convenience. Step inside, and you'll discover a well-appointed interior with an abundance of natural light, showcasing the open concept living. The spacious living area is ideal for both relaxation and entertainment.Retreat to the master suite, a private oasis offering his/her closet, jetted tub, and shower. The additional bedrooms are equally inviting and perfect for family, guests, or as a home office.Outside, you'll find a spacious backyard for outdoor gatherings, playtime, or gardening.
